metadata.name: The man (hud persian)
metadata.description:
This work is a combination of modern and futuristic art and old Iranian art, which is inspired by the Persian color of Caspian blue.
You see a male prisoner thinking of breaking the matrix.
This project has two other affiliated projects.
By purchasing the next two works, the value of this three-digit puzzle is multiplied.
